comments: Avdija (WAS) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: LaVine (CHI) throws an errant pass out of bounds.
Gibson (WAS) is slightly late to firm up in White's (CHI) path but marginal contact occurs as White goes over the pick.
Gibson (WAS) establishes himself in White's (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
White (CHI) legally contests Morris' (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Avdija (WAS) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during LaVine's (CHI) driving shot attempt. Wright (WAS) makes clean contact with the ball to block the shot.
Gibson (WAS) establishes himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Caruso (CHI) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
White (CHI) and Wright (WAS) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Kuzma's (WAS) shot attempt bounces out of bounds without anyone touching the ball. Possession is correctly awarded to the Bulls.
Gibson (WAS) and Vucevic (CHI) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Gibson (WAS) makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it from White (CHI) during the jump shot attempt.

Gibson (WAS) makes clean contact with the ball as he goes to the ground with White (CHI) during their pursuit for the loose ball. Any follow-through contact after the ball is dislodged is deemed incidental.
After the ball becomes loose, Williams (CHI) and Kuzma (WAS) come together and incidental contact occurs as they dive onto the floor in pursuit.

Caruso (CHI) loses control of the ball off of his knee during his attempted gather. He then goes to the floor and makes clean contact with the ball to take it away from Kuzma (WAS) before calling timeout.
Wright (WAS) legally contests LaVine's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Gibson (WAS) establishes himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Caruso (CHI) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
During the inbound, Vucevic (CHI) slightly extends his arms and marginal contact occurs with Avdija (WAS) as he briefly engages on the screen.
Wright (WAS) makes clean contact with the ball and then retracts his arm from LaVine's (CHI) path to avoid follow-through contact during the drive.
